#10125
@@yThe Stone Trap Chamber@@N~
The pyramid keeps its secrets with @@bsandstone@@N walls that press close on all sides, perfectly dressed blocks offering no crack for fingers and no purchase for climbing. @@yDust@@N sifts constantly through the shaft overhead, a pale golden fall of particulate that catches what little light exists and vanishes before it reaches the floor. The ceiling above is smooth and sheer, the shaft that delivered you here rising beyond any reasonable reach; whatever mechanism released that floor has sealed itself behind you. The @@bstone floor@@N slopes toward the center, worn smooth by the passage of countless others who triggered the same hidden plate or disguised cover. A shaft in the center of the floor descends into deeper darkness, carrying the cold exhalation of the @@bfoundation chambers@@N far below.
~
